---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About — Siddhesh Lakhani" 
  description="Full Stack Engineer from Mumbai — Linux enthusiast, Next.js developer, freelance builder."
  activePage="about"
>
  <div class="page-wrap">

    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="grid-bg"></div>
      <div class="about-hero-inner">
        <div class="section-tag">Know Me Better</div>
        <h1 class="section-h">Siddhesh<br><span style="color:var(--red)">Lakhani.</span></h1>
        <p class="section-sub">Full Stack Engineer · Linux Enthusiast · Freelance Developer · Building production-grade systems from Mumbai, India.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-wrap">
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <div class="t-dot red"></div>
          <div class="t-dot yellow"></div>
          <div class="t-dot green"></div>
          <span class="terminal-title">whoami.sh</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div><span class="t-comment">## >> whoami</span></div>
          <br>
          <div><span class="t-key">name&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-val">: Siddhesh Lakhani</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-key">role&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-val">: Full Stack Developer</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-key">location&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-val">: Mumbai, India</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-key">distro&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-green">: Arch Linux (btw, I use Arch)</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-key">wm&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-val">: DWM — riced &amp; suckless</span></div>
          <br>
          <div><span class="t-key">currently:</span></div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="t-key">learning&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-val">: Linux internals, K8s in prod</span></div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="t-key">obsessing </span><span class="t-val">: self-hosting everything possible</span></div>
          <br>
          <div><span class="t-key">values:</span></div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="t-red">- Minimalism in code AND design</span></div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="t-red">- Ship fast, optimize later</span></div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="t-red">- Own your stack, own your data</span></div>
          <br>
          <div><span class="t-key">contact&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-val">: lakhani.siddhesh@gmail.com</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-key">portfolio&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="t-green">: sidlakhani.in</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-section">
      <div class="bio-text">
        <div class="section-tag">My Story</div>
        <h2 class="section-h" style="margin-bottom:32px;">Minimalism<br>meets<br><span style="color:var(--red)">Performance.</span></h2>
        <p>I'm a passionate developer, tech enthusiast, and gamer who loves building cool stuff on the web. My journey started with <strong>JavaScript and TypeScript</strong>, crafting seamless, high-performance web apps with Next.js, React, and Tailwind CSS.</p>
        <p>Lately, I've been diving deeper into <strong>Linux</strong> — tweaking my workflow, optimizing performance, and exploring self-hosting. I'm currently running <strong>Garuda Linux</strong> for its speed and flexibility, and I run a custom <strong>DWM</strong> setup from scratch using the Suckless toolset.</p>
        <p>I believe in <strong>minimalism</strong>, both in design and functionality. That reflects in my work, whether it's a clean, efficient codebase or a sleek, no-frills portfolio that focuses on what truly matters. <strong>Problem-solving</strong> is what drives me — whether it's debugging tricky code, integrating APIs, or fine-tuning my system for peak efficiency.</p>
        <p>When I'm not coding, you'll probably find me immersed in <strong>gaming</strong>, vibing to music, or pushing my limits in sports. Tech, music, and competition fuel my energy, and I'm always up for a challenge.</p>
        <div class="bio-ctas">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Let's Build Together</a>
          <a href="/Resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-outline">Download Resume ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="values-list">
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">⚡</div>
            <div><div class="value-title">Ship Fast</div><div class="value-desc">Build MVPs, iterate quickly, optimize when needed. Don't over-engineer.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">🔐</div>
            <div><div class="value-title">Own Your Stack</div><div class="value-desc">Self-host when possible. Control your data, your infra, your systems.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">🧹</div>
            <div><div class="value-title">Minimalism First</div><div class="value-desc">Less noise, more signal — in code, in design, in tooling.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">🐧</div>
            <div><div class="value-title">Linux Purist</div><div class="value-desc">Arch + DWM. Full control. No bloat. Riced and suckless.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">🌐</div>
            <div><div class="value-title">Full-Stack Thinking</div><div class="value-desc">From DB schema to pixel-perfect UI — I think end-to-end.</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stack-section">
      <div class="section-tag">My Stack</div>
      <h2 class="section-h" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Technologies I<br><span style="color:var(--red)">Work With.</span></h2>
      <div class="stack-categories">
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Frontend</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Next.js</span><span class="stack-pill">React</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">TypeScript</span><span class="stack-pill">TailwindCSS</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Astro</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Backend</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">FastAPI</span><span class="stack-pill">Node.js</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Python</span><span class="stack-pill">Bun</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Express</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Databases</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">PostgreSQL</span><span class="stack-pill">MySQL</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Supabase</span><span class="stack-pill">Prisma</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Firebase</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Infra</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Docker</span><span class="stack-pill">Kubernetes</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Nginx</span><span class="stack-pill">Cloudflare</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Vercel</span><span class="stack-pill">Vultr</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ ML / CV</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">TensorFlow</span><span class="stack-pill">PyTorch</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">OpenCV</span><span class="stack-pill">Keras</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">scikit-learn</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-cat">
          <div class="stack-cat-label">→ Systems</div>
          <div class="stack-pills">
            <span class="stack-pill">Linux</span><span class="stack-pill">Rust</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">C++</span><span class="stack-pill">Bash</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Git</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="beyond-section">
      <div class="inner">
        <div class="section-tag" style="padding:0;">Beyond the Terminal</div>
        <h2 class="section-h" style="margin:12px 0 0;">Life outside<br><span style="color:var(--red)">the code.</span></h2>
        <div class="beyond-grid">
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-emoji">🎮</div>
            <div class="beyond-title">Gaming</div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">Competitive gamer. Clutch plays and game-winning moments fuel the same energy as solving hard bugs.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-emoji">🎵</div>
            <div class="beyond-title">Music</div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">Always vibing. Music is the background process running while I ship features.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-emoji">🏅</div>
            <div class="beyond-title">Sports</div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">Pushing limits physically. Competition and performance — on the field and in the terminal.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-card">
            <div class="beyond-emoji">🔧</div>
            <div class="beyond-title">Tinkering</div>
            <div class="beyond-desc">Linux ricing, self-hosting experiments, hardware tweaks. Always something running on a VPS.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-block">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <div class="section-tag" style="display:inline-block;margin-bottom:20px;">What's next?</div>
      <h2>Let's build<br><span style="color:var(--red)">something great.</span></h2>
      <p>Open to freelance projects, full-time roles, and interesting collaborations. Don't be a stranger.</p>
      <div class="btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="btn-outline">See My Work</a>
        <a href="/Resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-outline">Resume ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ABOUT PAGE */
.about-hero{
  padding:120px 52px 80px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.about-hero .grid-bg{opacity:.6;}
.about-hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:700px;}
.about-hero-inner .section-h{margin-top:12px;}
.about-hero-inner .section-sub{max-width:580px;}

/* WHOAMI TERMINAL */
.terminal-wrap{
  padding:0 52px 80px;
}
.terminal{
  background:var(--char2);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;
  max-width:680px;
}
.terminal-bar{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:12px 16px;
  background:var(--char3);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
}
.t-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;}
.t-dot.red{background:#ff5f57;}
.t-dot.yellow{background:#febc2e;}
.t-dot.green{background:#28c840;}
.terminal-title{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:4px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;}
.terminal-body{padding:24px 28px;font-family:'Space Grotesk',monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:1.9;}
.t-key{color:var(--muted);}
.t-val{color:var(--off);}
.t-red{color:var(--red);}
.t-green{color:#4ade80;}
.t-comment{color:#444a5e;font-style:italic;}

/* BIO SECTION */
.bio-section{
  padding:0 52px 80px;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;
}
.bio-text p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:18px;}
.bio-text p strong{color:var(--off);}
.bio-text .bio-ctas{margin-top:32px;display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

/* VALUES */
.values-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;}
.value-item{
  background:var(--char2);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:8px;padding:20px 22px;
  display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;
  transition:border-color .2s;
}
.value-item:hover{border-color:var(--red-border);}
.value-icon{
  font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;
}
.value-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--off);margin-bottom:4px;}
.value-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;}

/* STACK SECTION */
.stack-section{
  padding:0 52px 80px;
}
.stack-categories{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:40px;
}
.stack-cat{
  background:var(--char2);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:10px;padding:24px 22px;
  transition:border-color .2s;
}
.stack-cat:hover{border-color:var(--red-border);}
.stack-cat-label{
  font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:16px;
}
.stack-pills{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;}
.stack-pill{
  font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--off2);
  background:var(--char3);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  padding:5px 12px;border-radius:5px;
  transition:border-color .2s,color .2s;
}
.stack-pill:hover{border-color:var(--red);color:var(--off);}

/* BEYOND CODE */
.beyond-section{
  padding:0 52px 96px;
  background:var(--char2);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  margin:0 0 80px;
}
.beyond-section .inner{padding:80px 0;}
.beyond-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2px;margin-top:40px;}
.beyond-card{
  background:var(--char3);padding:28px 24px;
  border-left:1px solid var(--border);
}
.beyond-card:first-child{border-left:none;}
.beyond-emoji{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.beyond-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--off);margin-bottom:6px;}
.beyond-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;}

/* CTA BLOCK */
.cta-block{
  padding:0 52px 96px;text-align:center;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.cta-block .glow{
  position:absolute;bottom:-80px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:500px;height:280px;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,59,59,0.08) 0%,transparent 70%);
  pointer-events:none;
}
.cta-block h2{
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,52px);
  font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.5px;margin-bottom:16px;
}
.cta-block p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);max-width:420px;margin:0 auto 36px;line-height:1.7;}
.cta-block .btns{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

@media(max-width:900px){
  .about-hero,.bio-section,.stack-section,.cta-block,.terminal-wrap{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;}
  .bio-section{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .stack-categories{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .beyond-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .beyond-section{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;}
}
</style>
